{"tid":1640893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三對香港局勢致有人受傷感擔憂　盼相關人士克制","createTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T07:23:16.000Z","uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd3f6bd525b1a544fcbbd73468c42b28c93311d","tid":1640893,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"哇日本首相安倍晉三，評論到香港局勢，他對出現傷者的情況感到非常擔憂，希望相關人士保持克制及通過和平對話，解決目前情況。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485148-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485148-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=6e7ca6ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485148-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed20bf2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485148-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連日本都出聲了"},{"pid":"1f2620fff9bce66b9625fe518db3f09ad638b161","tid":1640893,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"fa6635bf5e8ac3c43855867902542b8b449a1e3a","tid":1640893,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d8c21f566117ded751bcdbc95a735abcf2bf962","tid":1640893,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"［圍觀師開工喇］大家組團去黨鐵站（文宣好機會）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640876</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d3a0cea4762ed0a3f342bd7428e49dfdc69bfd0a","tid":1640893,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd3f6bd525b1a544fcbbd73468c42b28c93311d","tid":1640893,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"哇日本首相安倍晉三，評論到香港局勢，他對出現傷者的情況感到非常擔憂，希望相關人士保持克制及通過和平對話，解決目前情況。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485148-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485148-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=6e7ca6ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485148-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed20bf2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485148-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連日本都出聲了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"不用理"},{"pid":"335f1eef32b5ff693ebf89ef60ec163f6e1634d4","tid":1640893,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"但安倍只係好輕描淡寫<br />\n唔敢得罪中國"},{"pid":"1453e85221269c2ae35667bfbde8f6b9968863c5","tid":1640893,"uid":259813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"335f1eef32b5ff693ebf89ef60ec163f6e1634d4","tid":1640893,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"但安倍只係好輕描淡寫<br />\n唔敢得罪中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"老實日本不嬲唔響咩人權之類度出聲<br />\n肯咁樣講一句都好領情啦"},{"pid":"32ee8e0935ff7f6a80cad6eaee67676f9748df8e","tid":1640893,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"335f1eef32b5ff693ebf89ef60ec163f6e1634d4","tid":1640893,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"但安倍只係好輕描淡寫<br />\n唔敢得罪中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"要引起日本民怨"}]}